title: 750 Premium Disinfectant Bulk Wipes – Sani Care Antibacterial Wipes for Retail and Travel Industries – Ideal Sanitising & Hygiene for Trolleys, Touch Screens and All Surface Sterilising
features: A bucket containing 750 premium Antibacterial, disinfectant Bulk Wipes, designed for effective and thorough Surface cleaning and sanitation in various environments.
Sani Care Swipes are tailored for use in the retail and travel industries, making them ideal for airports, hotels, shopping centres, and similar locations.
Versatile in application, these wipes can be used on a range of surfaces, including trolleys, touch screens, hands, and many other high-contact areas.
Formulated to effectively Sanitise, kill germs, bacteria, and viruses, ensuring that your environment remains safe, healthy, and hygienic at all times.
Designed for convenience and ease of use, simply pull out a wipe to start cleaning quickly and efficiently with minimal effort.
Perfect for high-traffic areas where maintaining cleanliness is crucial, such as busy public spaces where hygiene standards are a priority.
Crafted from high-quality materials that are safe for all surfaces and gentle on the skin, ensuring both effective cleaning and user comfort.
Helps to uphold a hygienic and germ-free environment, significantly reducing the risk of infections and illnesses by maintaining cleanliness.
Help save our future! Use 100% recyclable Sani Care Swipe wipes - upcycled and re-purposed after use.
